        </a> |
        <a href="tel:+12814882800">
          <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> (281) 488-2800
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-right">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> James Andersen, Attorney at Law. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
